town section
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a section of land (often an acre) within a planned town
Origin: [none]
Register: historical

Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: See also town acre; rural section
